---
<section class="py-32 bg-[#0B0C10] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-[#004E98]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-end">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-12 text-white">
          Planejamento que elimina o desperdício.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Metric 1 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:text-left gap-4 md:gap-6">
            <span class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-bold text-[#FBB03B]">85%</span>
            <div class="md:border-l border-white/20 md:pl-4">
              <p class="font-label text-xs uppercase text-white/50 tracking-widest mb-1">Mais de 85% de aproveitamento de cada chapa de MDF.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Metric 2 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:text-left gap-4 md:gap-6">
            <span class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-bold text-[#FBB03B]">0%</span>
            <div class="md:border-l border-white/20 md:pl-4">
              <p class="font-label text-xs uppercase text-white/50 tracking-widest mb-1">0% de surpresas no seu orçamento de materiais.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Metric 3 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:text-left gap-4 md:gap-6">
            <span class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-bold text-[#FBB03B]">60%</span>
            <div class="md:border-l border-white/20 md:pl-4">
              <p class="font-label text-xs uppercase text-white/50 tracking-widest mb-1">Até 60% de economia real em relação às lojas.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-container-high p-8 md:p-12 relative border border-white/5 rounded-sm">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-6xl mb-8" data-icon="inventory_2">inventory_2</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Pronto para otimizar seu investimento?</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-white/70 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Não compre móveis no escuro. Receba o projeto técnico completo e a lista exata para comprar direto da fábrica com segurança.
        </p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/5551996532525?text=Ol%C3%A1%20Willian%21%20Quero%20garantir%20um%20projeto%20100%25%20execut%C3%A1vel%20no%20Cortecloud%2C%20com%20plano%20de%20corte%20otimizado%20e%20zero%20margem%20de%20erro." class="w-full bg-[#FBB03B] text-black px-8 py-5 font-label font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-md shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Quero Orçar Meu Projeto
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="calculate">calculate</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
